b'' b'the simplest and cheapest soft uv bulb is an ar-1 argon bulb (or other argon' b'bulb). it works like a neon bulb except it glows purple. it will cause' b'stuff to fluoresce. it requires very little power, just a battery, an' b'oscillator, and a step-up transformer to about volts.' b'' b'electronic goldmine has several uv lamps, both as pre-built' b'units and kits. ask for their catalog.' 